              Automatic license <span class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-400 to-cyan-400 bg-clip-text text-transparent">assignment</span>
            </h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-8">
              Create rules that automatically assign licenses when devices are deployed or users are created. Link your Microsoft licenses directly to your device lifecycle—no manual provisioning required.
            </p>

            <div class="space-y-4">
              <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                <div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-blue-600/20 flex items-center justify-center text-blue-400 flex-shrink-0 mt-1">
                  <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7" />
                  </svg>
                </div>
                <div>
                  <h3 class="font-semibold text-white">Device Deployment Trigger</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Automatically assign licenses when a device status changes to deployed. Link Windows licenses to device deployment.</p>
